..................... </span><span style=\"color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">17</span></span></a></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt;\"><a href=\"#_Toc259807192\"><span><font color=\"#0000ff\">十九、客户方案拼接功能及系统组成</font><span style=\"color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">............................................................................................. </span><span style=\"color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">18</span></span></a></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt;\"><a href=\"#_Toc259807193\"><span><font color=\"#0000ff\">二十、客户方案拼接单元技术指标及系统设备清单</font><span style=\"color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none;\">........................................................................ 19</span></span></a></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><br clear=\"all\" />\r\n<br />\r\n</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><a name=\"_Toc164589283\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">一、前言：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">SLCD液晶拼接墙<span>2007年推出的高科技产品。公司引进世界顶级液晶面板生产商韩国三星公司最新DID液晶显示技术，原装进口SLCD液晶拼接屏，利用美国PW公司最先进的液晶拼接控制及高速图像处理技术，内置自主研发的液晶拼接控制器，实现了多路高速视频信号的处理，以高清晰度、高亮度与高色域的液晶显示技术、嵌入式硬件拼接技术、多屏图像处理技术、信号切换技术等合为一体，形成一个具有高亮度、高清晰度、低功耗、高寿命、先进的液晶拼接墙显示系统。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">公司生产的<span>SLCD液晶拼接墙，画面宏大、色彩艳丽，清晰度高，视觉冲击强烈，具有很好的展示、演示、广告、宣传的效果；安装简便、不受空间限制。SLCD液晶拼接墙被广泛应用于：视频监控、电信、公共事业、过程处理、交通控制、安防监控以及国防、舞台娱乐、电视演播厅、股票证券、大型会展、商场、银行、办公大厅、公司迎客屏、专卖店、调度指挥等。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><a name=\"_Toc164589284\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">二、液晶拼接墙的屏幕&mdash;&mdash;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">SLCD</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">液晶拼接屏</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">SLCD液晶拼接墙采用原装进口<span>SLCD窄边液晶屏，具有高亮度、高对比度、更好的彩色饱和度、更宽的视角、更好的可靠性、影像稳定不闪烁、较长的使用寿命等特征。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b>★高亮度</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">SLCD采用的<span>LCD<strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">液晶拼接单元</span></strong>具有更高的亮度，可以达到700 cd/m<sup><font size=\"2\">2</font></sup>。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">★<strong><span>高对比度</span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SLCD</span>采用的LCD<strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">液晶拼接单元</span></strong>的对比度与普通的液晶屏相比，要高出一倍以上，是一般背投的二～三倍。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">★<strong><span>更好的彩色饱和度</span></strong></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">拼接单元采用先进的</span></strong>色彩校准技术，除了对静止画面进行色彩校准外，还能对动态画面进行色彩的校准，确保了画面输出的精确和稳定。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 46pt; text-indent: -18pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span>★<span style=\"font: 7pt/normal &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><strong>更宽的视角</strong></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">拼接<strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">单元采用了先进的</span></strong>图像调整技术，可视角度可达178&deg;。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">★<strong><span>更好的可靠性</span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>家用电视、PC所采用的液晶屏不能负荷24小时连续使用，SLCD <strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">液晶拼接单元</span></strong>为监视器所设计，可以24小时连续工作。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">★<b>影像稳定不闪烁</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">由于<span>LCD每一个点在接收到信号后就一直保持那种色彩和亮度，而不像CRT那样需要不断刷新亮点。因此，LCD亮度均匀、画质高而且绝对不会闪烁。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 0.05pt; text-align: left; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"left\">★<strong><span>更长使用寿命</span></strong></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: left; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"left\"><span>拼接</span><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">单元所用的</span></strong><span>背光源使用寿命均可达</span>6<span>万小时以上，这就确保了拼接幕墙使用的每片液晶屏在长时间使用后的亮度、对比度和色度的一致性并且确保拼接墙的使用寿命。</span><a name=\"_Toc164589285\"></a></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">三、<span>SLCD液晶拼接墙的特征</span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: blue;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><b><span style=\"color: red;\">拼接单元背部图片</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong>★高清晰度、高亮度、高色域</strong><b><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>清晰度、亮度、色彩饱和度是液晶的三个重要性能指标，<strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">公司生产的<span>SLCD液晶拼接</span></span></strong>单元具有高清晰度、高亮度、高色域的特点。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong>★窄边设计</strong><b><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>液晶由于使用背光灯管作为发光源，其边缘一般较宽，<span>40英寸普通液晶屏其边距宽度超过30mm，如果用于拼接，拼接缝隙至少达60mm，影响视觉效果。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">SLCD</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">液晶</span></strong>拼接墙采用液晶屏经过了窄边结构设计的<span>DID屏，边缘缩减一倍以上，用于拼接不影响视觉效果。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b>40</b><b>寸窄边液晶拼接拼接单元尺寸及拼接缝隙说明<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 14.25pt;\">\r\n            <td width=\"157\" style=\"padding: 0cm 5.4pt; border: 1pt solid windowtext; width: 117.75pt; height: 14.25pt; background-color: transparent;\"><br />\r\n            &nbsp;\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\">SLCD液晶单元</div>\r\n            <br />\r\n            &nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width=\"156\" style=\"border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: windowtext windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 117pt; height: 14.25pt; background-color: transparent;\"><br />\r\n            &nbsp;\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\">单元外形尺寸</div>\r\n            <br />\r\n            &nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width=\"288\" style=\"border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: windowtext windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 216pt; height: 14.25pt; background-color: transparent;\"><br />\r\n            &nbsp;\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\">拼接缝隙</div>\r\n            <br />\r\n            &nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 31.5pt;\">\r\n            <td width=\"157\" style=\"border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 117.75pt; height: 31.5pt; background-color: transparent;\"><br />\r\n            &nbsp;\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\">40寸<span>(DID屏) 16:9</span></div>\r\n            <br />\r\n            &nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width=\"156\" style=\"border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 117pt; height: 31.5pt; background-color: transparent;\"><br />\r\n            &nbsp;\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\">911.7<br />\r\n            &nbsp; (W)&times;522.9 (H)&times;100 (D)mm</div>\r\n            <br />\r\n            &nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td width=\"288\" style=\"border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) windowtext windowtext rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 216pt; height: 31.5pt; background-color: transparent;\"><br />\r\n            &nbsp;\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\">上下拼接缝≦18mm&nbsp;左右拼接缝≦18mm</div>\r\n            <br />\r\n            &nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 6pt 0cm; text-indent: 28.05pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">★</span></strong><strong>拼接方式任意选择</strong></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 28.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">SLCD</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">液晶</span></strong>拼接墙，拼接数量任意选择（行<span>(m) X 列(n)），屏的大小亦有多种选择（目前<strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">SLCD</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">液晶</span></strong>拼接墙只对19</span>〞、40〞、46〞进行拼接），以满足不同使用场合的需求。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 28.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong>★灵活多变的拼接显示组合功能 </strong></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 28.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">SLCD</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">液晶</span></strong>拼接墙可以根据不同用户的要求进行个性化设计，可以选择单屏显示、整屏显示、任意组合显示等功能。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">★先进的屏幕参数高校功能</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">针对液晶拼接幕墙使用液晶屏和驱动电路可能存在参数不一致问题，SLCD液晶拼接墙系统中采用了亮度、对比度、色度、白平衡的调整功能，调试后，参数自动保存，从而保证了整幅拼接屏幕的色彩一致性和亮度的均匀性。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">★环保健康 </span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">与背投式（包括CRT背投、DLP等）拼接墙相比，LCD液晶拼接墙发热量小、无辐射、无闪烁、不伤眼、不含有害物质（如铅、汞、镉和铬等），是新一代的环保健康拼接墙。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">★稳定运行寿命长，维护成本低 </span></strong><b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">液晶显示技术是目前最优异的平板显示技术之一，SLCD拼接墙使用的液晶拼接单元的灯管具有超过60000小时的使用寿命且长时间工作后图像稳定没任何变化。液晶显示技术没有任何需要定期更换的耗材设备，所以维护、维修成本极低。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21.1pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">★多种安装方式 </span></strong></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">公司生产的SLCD拼接墙可以嵌入落地电视墙，或者壁挂，或者吊挂。拼接墙结构件采用全钢结构，坚固牢靠，安装简单方便，整体结构紧凑大方、节省空间。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><a name=\"_Toc164589286\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">四、<span>SLCD液晶拼接墙的特点</span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 20.15pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span>①<span style=\"font: 7pt/normal &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">SLCD</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">液晶拼接墙采用了硬件与软件结合的方式来实现拼接。软件操作方便</span></strong>易用。用户只须经过简单培训，即可操作。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 20.15pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span>②<span style=\"font: 7pt/normal &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</span></span>系统方案确定前，可根据用户要求来任意修改操作软件所控制的不同模式。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 20.15pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span>③<span style=\"font: 7pt/normal &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</span></span>硬件部分采用嵌入式板卡处理，图像处理速度快。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 20.15pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span>④<span style=\"font: 7pt/normal &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</span></span>用户不需要支付软件费用，总体成本较低。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 20.15pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span>⑤<span style=\"font: 7pt/normal &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</span></span>拼接墙体积小，重量轻，结构简单紧凑，同时也提高了系统的稳定性和可靠性。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><a name=\"_Toc164589287\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">五、<span>SLCD液晶拼接墙方案可行性</span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">液晶拼接墙既可以采用小屏拼接、也可以采用大屏拼接，拼接可任意组合（M&times;N）。我们会根据不同的客户对拼接系统提出的系统规模、尺寸和应用要求，选择合适的产品和拼接方式，提出具体实施方案，满足系统的应用需求。<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">我们将根据客户对输入信号的要求，选择不同的图像处理系统，实现VGA、BNC复合视频、S-VIDEO（可选）、YPBPR/YCBCR（可选）或DVI（可选）信号输入，满足不同使用场合，不同信号输入的需求。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">通过RS-232通讯接口来控制图像控制器以实现图像任意组合显示模式的切换、各种信号源的切换、图像拉伸、叠加等。 </span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">公司可根据客户的不同需求，设计个性化系统，提供不同的实施方案和技术支持。</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><a name=\"_Toc164589288\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">六、<span>SLCD液晶拼接墙系统的可靠性</span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal;\">SLCD</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal;\">液晶拼接墙所用的液晶拼接单元是为专业</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">监控所设计的液晶屏，拼接单元可一天24小时连续工作，具有可靠性、稳定性高等特点，以保证系统稳定可靠地运行。由于低功耗、重量轻、寿命长，无辐射等特点，使液晶拼接墙可靠性极高，一般可正常工作6万小时以上。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><a name=\"_Toc164589289\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">七、<span>SLCD液晶拼接墙系统的经济性</span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">下面让我们来比较一下等离子拼接墙、DLP拼接墙与液晶拼接墙的价格及维护成本： </span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">等离子拼接墙价格高，一平方米的价格高达十几万，且由于存在等离子烙印问题，不适宜在显示静态图像的场合使用，总体性价比低。而DLP拼接墙价格也比较高，一年就灯泡的更换费用高达几千块每个单元，一个幕墙加起少则一二万，多则七八万，几年维护的费用惊人，总体性价比低。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">液晶以其卓越的性能，合理的价格，且高达<span>6万小时的使用寿命，质量稳定，维护费用低，无疑是性价比最好的大屏幕拼接产品。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><a name=\"_Toc164589290\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">八、系统示意图</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: center; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\"><a name=\"_Toc164589291\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: center; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: center; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: center; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><a name=\"_Toc259807178\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">九、液晶拼接墙的基本构成</span></strong></a></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal;\">液晶拼接墙墙的基本构成：</span></strong></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">SLCD</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">液晶拼接单元、图像拼接控制处理器（内置在屏的背部）、拼接控制软件、各种线材、机柜等；用户自配：控制电脑（配置任意，主板带RS-232通讯接口）</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><a name=\"_Toc164589292\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">十、<span>SLCD液晶拼接幕墙实物照片</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">与工程案例</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: center; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: center; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\"><b><span style=\"color: red;\">SLCD 40</span></b><b><span style=\"color: red;\">〞DID 3&times;4 </span></b><b><span style=\"color: red;\">液晶拼接墙 实物图</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 13pt 0cm;\"><b><font size=\"5\">各系列安装示意图： </font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><span>拼接屏外框处理后着色为黑色，机柜着色为深灰色、拼接屏与机柜颜色搭配起来，美观而大方。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b><span>安装方式：</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 13pt 0cm;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">监控系统方案</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b><span>案例一</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>405</b><b><span>系列和</span></b><b>40B</b><b><span>系列组合拼接墙。</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b><span>根据项目需求，选择任意组合拼接墙</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 15.75pt; text-indent: -15.75pt;\">1<span>、可选择</span>3*4<span>组合拼接墙，周边</span>8<span>台</span>4000<span>系列</span>4<span>合</span>1<span>单体显示（带拼接），就有</span>32<span>路通道显示，中间</span>4<span>台用</span>5000<span>系列，可大屏幕拼接，显示</span>9<span>路重要通道或任意拼接显示，可切换硬盘录像机画面实时监控和大屏幕回放硬盘录像机图像。不用配</span>VGA<span>矩阵拼接，共有</span>36<span>路通道显示。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 15.75pt; text-indent: -15.75pt;\">2<span>、可选择</span>4*5<span>组合拼接墙，周边</span>11<span>台</span>4000<span>系列</span>4<span>合</span>1<span>单体显示（带拼接），就有</span>44<span>路通道显示，中间用</span>9<span>台</span>5000<span>系列，可大屏幕拼接，显示</span>9<span>路或任意拼接显示，可切换硬盘录像机画面实时监控和任意拼接显示回放硬盘录像机图像，不用配</span>VGA<span>矩阵拼接，共有</span>53<span>路通道显示。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: 15.75pt;\">PC<span>机中控软件&mdash;&mdash;设置液晶拼接墙，任意拼接、各屏参数，各功能显示等。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span>或用遥控器，可不用</span>PC<span>机中控软件，直接遥控设置。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><span>灵活多变的拼接显示组合功能，根据用户使用环境要求进行个性设计，实现的模式简单举例说明如下：</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b><span>系统示意图：</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b><span>案例二</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: 15.5pt;\"><b>2000</b><b><span>系列液晶拼接电视墙</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: 15.45pt;\"><span>可选择</span> 2*2 <span>、</span>3*3<br />\r\n<span>、</span>3*4 <span>、</span>3*7<span>等任意组合。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 10.3pt;\"><span>前端摄象机视频型号&mdash;&mdash;经过分配器信号</span>1<span>分为</span>2<span>&mdash;&mdash;</span>1<span>路进</span>AV<span>视频矩阵，另</span>1<span>路进入硬盘录象机实时录象，&mdash;&mdash;视频矩阵控制、切换视频信号在拼接墙任意显示。&mdash;&mdash;硬盘录象机</span>VGA<span>信号输出，经过</span>VGA<span>矩阵接入拼接墙显示，可任意切换拼接显示。大屏幕回放录象信息。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent: 10.3pt;\">PC<span>机中控软件&mdash;&mdash;设置液晶拼接墙，任意拼接、各屏参数，各功能显示等。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><span>灵活多变的拼接显示组合功能，根据用户使用环境要求进行个性设计，实现的模式简单举例说明如下：</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 31.6pt; text-indent: -31.6pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">特别说明：</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 15.75pt; text-indent: -15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">、任意组合模式中的任意信号切换，如需切换不同的视频信号，则需通过视频矩阵进行切换来实现（用户可自行配备视频矩阵，要求输出信号要达到拼接屏的数量以上）需切换不同的</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">VGA</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">信号，则需通过</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">VGA</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">矩阵进行切换来实现。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 31.5pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">拼接系统默认为用户自配视频矩阵与</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">VGA</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">矩阵。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 33.7pt; text-indent: -21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">注：系统中有多路</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">VGA</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">信号，并且都需要连入系统实现拼接大屏幕显示，则需要配用</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">VGA</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">矩阵，且输出路数要达到拼接屏的数量以上</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 31.5pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">、切换不同模式要通过软件进行控制，本拼接系统开发中控软件提供给用户，只需配置任意配置的电脑来进行操作。拼接系统默认为用户自配电脑。（要求配有</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">RS232</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">通讯接口）</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-align: center; layout-grid-mode: char;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><a name=\"_Toc164589293\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">十一、拼接墙显示尺寸及外观尺寸计算</span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">液晶拼接墙的大小由幕墙单元的个数 (长M&times;高N) 和单元的尺寸来计算。例如 3x4 40&Prime;拼接墙共12个40&Prime;拼接单元组成，40&Prime;拼接单元的（长： 911.7 (W)&times;（高：522.9mm ）;拼接墙的长<br />\r\n4x911.7=3646.8mm 高3x522.9=1568.7mm，使用时可根据安装环境选择不同的安装方式时再加上边框及立式底座的尺寸，便可得到幕墙的外观尺寸。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; text-indent: 21pt; layout-grid-mode: char;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt; line-height: normal; layout-grid-mode: char;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><a name=\"_Toc164589294\"><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">十二、</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">中控软件及系统环境要求</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 5pt 0cm 0pt -27pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span>超强中控软件：</span></b><span>全系列产品皆可使用为娱乐行业、安防行业量身订做的中控软件集中统一控制，可进行手动</span>\\<span>定时</span>\\<span>巡航</span>\\<span>报警预案设定和万花筒演示、智能温控及报警、通讯故障自动检测、框架补偿及遮挡选择等功能，带来极大的便利性并实现丰富的增值功能。该软件结合工程安装上的特点开发完成。采用目前软件设计的前沿理念</span>,<span>摒弃传统拼接器控制软件复杂的调试要求，</span> <span>对拼接过程实现自动运算</span>,<span>对窗口控制过程采用所见即所得的操作界面，避免传统的拼接器软件繁琐复杂的预设过程；简单易用！</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 5pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">※</span></b><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">支持液晶单元的所有功能操作全面　灵活　快捷的信号源管理图像拼接　数字漫游跨屏显示管理</span></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><b>&nbsp;</b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br clear=\"ALL\" />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 13pt 0cm;\"><b><font size=\"5\"><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">系统环境设计和要求</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 31.5pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">为保证项目实施的顺利进行，保护系统设备的正常工作</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">,</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">设备的安装现场须满足以下环境条件：</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 13pt 0cm;\"><b><font size=\"4\"><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">、安装要求</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 31.5pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1）、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">安装地面要求平整结实，承重力强，不变形。保证上屏与下屏之间没有压力</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）、基座一般直接与抗静电地板接触，以保证地面长期承重受力不变形。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 26.25pt; text-indent: -26.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）、安装在墙壁上则要注意墙壁的承载能力和墙体的结实程度，而且墙壁和屏幕之间要留有大于</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">20CM</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">的散热空间以保证热量的排出。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 13pt 0cm;\"><b><font size=\"4\"><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">、操作控制台（室）装修及设备位置要求</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 27.1pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）、操作控制电脑的位置应在拼接屏幕的正对面，保持一定的观看距离，要求操作员可以方便直观的看到拼接屏的操作。如果有专门隔断的操作控制室，则操作控制室与大屏显示室之应有透明玻璃，方便操作员的观看。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 31.5pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）、控制电脑应尽可能位于拼接屏的正对面方向，并与拼接屏有合适的距离，以便于调试、色彩调整等操作。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 13pt 0cm;\"><b><font size=\"4\"><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">、走线及线槽要求</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 27.1pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）、弱电线缆（</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">VGA</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">、视频、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">RS-232</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">串口、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">DVI</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">信号连接线等）应与强电线缆隔开走线，避免信号干扰。如果是用走线槽，则不能共用一个走线槽，应分不同的走线槽分开走线。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 27.1pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）、如果是抗静电地板，则走线出口处应开孔，留线缆出口。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 13pt 0cm;\"><b><font size=\"4\"><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">、空调要求</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 27.1pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）、拼接屏背后的维修通道内要有良好的温度控制和散热措施。如果是中央空调应有空调进、出风口，如果没有中央空调，应加设专门的空调，空调功率大小视大屏规模而定。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 27.1pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">、维修通道内温度与拼接屏控制室房间温度应可控制并基本保持相同</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 13pt 0cm;\"><b><font size=\"4\"><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">、供电电源</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 9.05pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">考虑到系统可能会遇到特殊情况会发生断点再通电的电流冲击，拼接单元本身具备电源保护设计，保证了设备的正常安全的运行。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 27.1pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">系统的电源为</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">AC 220V &plusmn;5%</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">；用有保护接地线的三眼插座；插座数与拼接屏数有关。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 27.1pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">拼接系统和图像控制器及控制</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">PC</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">等要求同相供电。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 27.1pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">电源电压要稳定，可靠，特别防止断电后立即加电，因此，原则上要求拼接系统的电源必须经过相应功率</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">UPS</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">供电。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 27.1pt; text-indent: -31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">系统设备要有良好的接地，接地电阻</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&lt;2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&Omega;，保证遇到雷击等特殊状况时设备不损坏。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 13pt 0cm;\"><b><font size=\"4\"><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height: 172%; font-size: 10.5pt;\">、系统环境</span></font></b></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 9.05pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）．拼接系统的背面是维修通道，维修通道宽度一般不小于</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">0.60</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">米，壁装安装则要求安装是设计好可方便维护的灵活固定支架。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 9.05pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）．大屏房间要求有较好的温度和湿度控制。工作环境温度为</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">23</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">℃</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&plusmn;5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">℃，相对湿度</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">20%-80%</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">。拼接背后要有通风。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 9.05pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）．拼接屏房间要求保持干净，防尘。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 7.8pt 0cm 7.8pt 9.05pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">）．消防喷头尽可能远离拼接墙</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">并且要用喷雾灭火剂。</span></div>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>','images/201305/thumb_img/2142_thumb_G_1368402287350.jpg','images/201305/goods_img/2142_G_1368402287618.jpg','images/201305/source_img/2142_G_1368402287449.jpg','1','','1','1','0','39','1368402287','100','0','1','1','0','0','0','1371436248','0','','0','0','0','0');
