x; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/840150749/T2e58lXdXNXXXXXXXX_!!840150749.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/840150749/T2ds8TXoxcXXXXXXXX_!!840150749.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/840150749/T2Z0pTXnBcXXXXXXXX_!!840150749.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#aa0000\" size=\"2\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><font size=\"2\">金属外壳 诠释简约风尚</font></strong></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#aa0000\" size=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(106,168,79)\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\"><font size=\"2\">　　不管是一键风格，还是深藏不露的内敛派，极致简约的设计几乎是目前潮流数码产品的共通点，引领着未来电子产品外形设计的发展趋势。作为素有设计界的&ldquo;奥斯卡&rdquo;之称的红点设计大奖(Red dot design award)2012年的获得者之一，金士顿DTSE9简约却很出众!</font></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#aa0000\" size=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68,68,68)\"><font size=\"2\">在外观上，它采用了通体淡银色的时尚金属外壳，棱角十足的USB接口与盘身尾部结实的大圆环设计，带来简约的造型感和坚固的概念化风格。尤其是尾部的圆环，不仅堪称整体设计的点睛之笔，让闪存盘袖珍的体积充满灵感和变化，还能搭配钥匙环、挂坠等，携带方便。</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#aa0000\" size=\"2\"><span style=\"color: rgb(106,168,79)\"><font size=\"2\">金士顿DTSE9盘身印有产品型号和容量，小巧的无盖帽设计，看似简单却别有匠心，不仅延续了金士顿以往的风格，不容易造成使用中盖帽的丢失，也让操作更为便利，为都市忙碌生活减压、提速。</font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#aa0000\" size=\"2\"><font size=\"2\"><b>超薄设计 超极本、平板最in搭配</b></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#aa0000\" size=\"2\"><font size=\"2\">　　&ldquo;轻薄&rdquo;同样是金士顿DTSE9的一大特点。很多拥有超薄笔记本</font><font size=\"2\">的用户或许都遇到过这样的尴尬：闪存盘身材太&ldquo;壮硕&rdquo;，超薄本本放在桌面上，再搭配一块较厚的闪存盘，还要在本本下面垫一本厚厚的书才能使用&hellip;&hellip;</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#aa0000\" size=\"2\"><font size=\"2\">随着超极本、平板电脑的流行，闪存盘轻薄化已经成为必然趋势，金士顿DTSE9正是超极本用户的最佳移动存储配件，让随行的商务应用更加轻松有型!</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#aa0000\" size=\"2\"><font size=\"2\">　　它不足5 mm的盘身厚度(39.00mm x 12.35mm x 4.55mm)，可以轻松的与超极本、超薄笔记本</font><font size=\"2\">相搭配。简洁的设计风格与超极本等产品的设计思路和谐统一，搭配在一起十分自然，不显突兀。同时，金士顿DTSE9还能与具备USB接口的平板电脑搭配使用，外形匹配、不占空间，还能为主流16G</font><font size=\"2\">内存</font><font size=\"2\">的平板电脑扩容更多存储空间;对于那些不具备标准USB接口的平板用户来说，可以准备好一根简单的T型OTG线即可方便使用;如果是iPad用户的话，在产品越狱的前提下，可以搭配相机套件使用，也很方便。</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#aa0000\" size=\"2\"><font size=\"2\"><b>　主流容量 匹配多应用系统</b></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#aa0000\" size=\"2\"><font size=\"2\">金士顿DTSE9闪存盘具备当前主流的存储容量，共有8G、16G两种选择。尤其是对于平板电脑用户来说，一般16G空间存储几部电影、一些音乐、照片与应用就会显得很紧张。金士顿DTSE9能够最大为平板扩容16G的存储空间，能够存储600M大小的影片27部之多;4M大小的mp3歌曲4000多首;百万级像素的JPEG照片3200多张;还可存储1MB 大小的Word/Excel文件12000多份;5M大小PPT文件2400多份，让随身的娱乐更加丰富，对超级本用户来说，也是移动办公的好帮手。</font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>','images/201305/thumb_img/2172_thumb_G_1368732674352.jpg','images/201305/goods_img/2172_G_1368732674892.jpg','images/201305/source_img/2172_G_1368732674310.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1368732674','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1396303124','32','','0','0','0','0');
