der-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" src=\"http://2d.zol-img.com.cn/product/78_240x180/743/ce2GcpYJMKZu.jpg\" /></a><br />\r\n飞利浦SPA1301音箱</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一款音箱的操作性同样重要，在低音炮的前面板上带有小小的装饰块，带有飞利浦的品牌标志，上面设计有<a class=\"hui14_line\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\" href=\"http://power.zol.com.cn/\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">电源</font></a>开关和音量调节的一体式旋钮，操作可以简单完成，并带有绿色的电源指示灯，倒相孔前置。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/picture_index_781/index7801744.shtml\"><img alt=\"高性价比选择 飞利浦SPA1301音箱简评 \" width=\"240\" height=\"180\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" src=\"http://2e.zol-img.com.cn/product/78_240x180/744/ceIIr6j3In49Y.jpg\" /></a>&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/picture_index_781/index7801745.shtml\"><img alt=\"高性价比选择 飞利浦SPA1301音箱简评 \" width=\"240\" height=\"180\" style=\"border-b