b(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img5.pcpop.com/ArticleImages/500x375/2/2341/002341415.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">顶置控制面板</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 魔甲兵机箱给人第一感觉就是源自魔兽战甲设计，全黑武装，棱角分明充满动感的外观，从设计之初就已经将魔甲的概念融入其中，延续CM STORM系列产品的游戏设计风格。前面板由8块菱角分明的冲孔网面板组成，让整台机箱产生&ldquo;魔装甲&rdquo;效果，每块魔甲的菱角部件都配置了防尘棉，细节之处也为玩家想到了更多实用性，增加防尘效果；酷冷至尊的LOGO设计在机箱正面板底部，与整台机箱搭配感觉上也非常协调。整体感觉稳如泰山，非常扎实，名副其实的&ldquo;不动如山&rdquo;。酷冷在设计上为玩家精心增加顶部可提式把手，采用了防滑橡胶质感涂层，携带方便，随时随地移动机箱，与真兄弟并肩作战。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img5.pcpop.com/ArticleImages/500x375/2/2341/002341416.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">魔甲兵侧面图</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 顶端控制面板上前置I/O接口装备1个USB3.0及2个USB2.0数据交换接口，让数据交换更快捷，足以满足任何数据交换及高端USB3.0设备需求。麦克风、耳机接口一应俱全，满足战队联络及语音交流之便捷。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-to