nt-size: 18px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"547\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/01.jpg\" /></a></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">酷冷至尊COSMOS II的包装采用了红+紫的配色设计，黑色与COSMOS II的整体黑色的外观相符、极具神秘感，而紫色则是酷冷至尊包装的原有风格。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"622\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/02.jpg\" /></a></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">酷冷至尊COSMOS II的主体外观预览</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">酷冷至尊COSMOS II是酷冷至尊全新推出的一款顶级全塔机箱，该机箱是COSMOS的第二代大改款产品，相较多年前的COSMOS一代产品无论是架构还是设计均获有了质的改变，近乎完美的架构更能满足广大高端<a target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><u style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">用户</strong></u></a>愈发挑剔的使用需求。COSMOS II外形尺寸为344(W) x 704(H) x 644(D)mm ，巨大的尺寸让送快递的派件员的都大为感慨，同时相较老款产品尺寸的改变也说明了这是一款全新设计的机箱。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"606\" height=\"455\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/01.png\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">产品规格列表，可以看到这款机箱拥有超强的兼容性</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<table border=\"0\" style=\"border-bottom-color: black; text-align: left; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); border-top-color: black; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; border-spacing: 0px; width: 660px; display: table; border-collapse: separate; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; height: 1509px; color: rgb(64,64,64); border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n            <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n            <h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">酷冷至尊COSMOS II外观多角度赏析</span></span></h2>\r\n            <p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"400\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/03.jpg\" /></a></span></span></p>\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">酷冷至尊COSMOS II的左侧侧板及前面板</span></span>\r\n            <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">作为一款以跑车题材为主题元素的GAMING机箱，COSMOS II在外观设计上保留了老款COSMOS圆润的流线型风格，同时继承下来还有机箱顶部及底部的金属杆，而这也赋予了这款机箱与众不同的感觉。在箱体外部材质方面COSMOS II采用了ABS工程塑料包覆铝板的独特设计，这种设计不仅保持了纯铝面板的金属质感，同时还继承了塑料件外形可设计性强的特点。在整体风格上COSMOS II虽然外形圆润，但不失稳重和阳刚霸气，相信其中不小的原因是因为这款机型硕大的体型和材质的原因吧。</span></span></p>\r\n            <p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"399\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/04.jpg\" /></a></span></span></p>\r\n            <span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">酷冷至尊COSMOS II的后面板及右侧侧板</span></span>\r\n            <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">从设计上来看，COSMOS II采用了全塔式设计，这点仅从机箱后面板PCI扩展位的数量上就可以看到一些端倪，10+1位PCI设计轻松满足那些游戏发烧友组建多显卡游戏平台，而14cm 大尺寸后置系统风扇则再次向我们展示了这款机箱体型的硕大，水冷孔和下置电源位在这里就不做过多介绍了。</span></span></p>\r\n            <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">COSMOS II的右侧侧板采用了与左侧侧板相同的主题元素设计，区别仅是散热孔的造型，究竟这款机箱这里的风道环境如何呢？要知道这个答案还需对其内部设计进行详细的研究。</span></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">酷冷至尊COSMOS II的梦幻前面板解析</h2>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"535\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/05.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">从上图可以看到，COSMOS II前面板的外观设计非常梦幻，覆铝材质的盾形挡不仅板质感十足，再配合大面积高品质的金属冲孔网板后，营造出了一种非常强烈的科技感，最大程度的体现了酷冷至尊的工业设计水平。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/06.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">工程塑料覆铝设计的盾形挡板经喷砂阳极化处理后呈磨砂质感，手感一流质感十足</strong></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/08.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">COSMOS II面板上的酷冷至尊Logo特写，金属材质质感十足，起到了画龙点睛的作用</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/07.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">面板下方大面积高品质的金属冲孔网板同样质感十足，大面积金属冲孔网板不仅外观硬朗，同时还能起到很好的辅助散热的作用。另外从上图可以看到，在网板的内部还衬有菱形设计的支撑网格，给人的感觉就像梦幻跑车的发动机进气格栅，非常符合这款机箱的设计主题。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/09.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">COSMOS II的盾形光驱挡板采用了下滑式设计，用户仅需在把手处轻轻向下一拨，盾形挡板即可匀速缓慢的滑下，颇具梦幻色彩，同时手感也很不错。打开挡板后可以看到，在其内部是3个5.25寸光驱位以及1个支持热插拔的双位3.5寸硬盘仓，这些仓位均采用了免工具解锁设计，极大的简化了磁盘的拆装。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/010.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">3.5寸硬盘安装示范，其设计与很多服务器机箱的硬盘位设计相似，同时左侧的仓门锁则更大程度的增强了数据盘的安全性。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">酷冷至尊COSMOS II的梦幻顶盖</h2>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"384\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/013.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">COSMOS II的梦幻顶盖外观预览，流线型设计与其跑车的主题元素非常相符</span></p>\r\n<h2 align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"399\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/011.jpg\" /></a></h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">COSMOS II的梦幻顶盖外观多角度赏析</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"399\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/012.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">COSMOS II的梦幻顶盖外观多角度赏析</span></p>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">COSMOS II的梦幻顶盖外观细节解析</h2>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/014.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">COSMOS II顶盖的前端拥有一个与面板的盾形挡板材质及结构相似的盖板，这个盖板同样采用了滑盖式设计，用户仅需轻轻向后一推即可打开盖板，手感就像滑盖手机。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/015.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">打开盖板后可以看到这款机箱的开关重启键以及风扇灯光及风扇转速调速器面板，面板的材质为铝，手感就像某些手机的设计，虽然现在流行触屏手机，但这种设计在机箱中仍属首例。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"432\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/016.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">前置IO接口位于机箱顶部的前端，顶置式设计有利于习惯把机箱放在台面下的用户操作电脑。在IO接口的配备方面COSMOS II为我们提供了丰富的接口配备，可以看到除了传统的音频接口以外，COSMOS II还拥有4个USB2.0以及2个USB3.0接口，另外还有一组e-SATA接口，无论是种类还是数量都足以满足用户的日常使用。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"432\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/017.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">COSMOS II外观细节赏析，相信从上图就可以了解到这款机箱的工业设计是多么的复杂&mdash;&mdash;金属冲孔网板、ABS工程塑料、拉丝覆铝面板、喷砂覆铝面板，酷冷至尊通过这些不同材质面板的结合打造出了一款极富科技感的高品质机箱，而这也很大程度的反映了酷冷至尊的工业设计水平。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"432\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/018.jpg\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">箱尾散热孔细节多角度赏析</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"378\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/019.jpg\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">从COSMOS一代上传承下来的提手特写，由全铝打造，经喷砂阳极化处理后质感十足</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"549\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/021.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">酷冷至尊COSMOS II的特色侧板多角度赏析</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"474\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/022.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">酷冷至尊COSMOS II的侧板呈立体状，质感十足，ABS工程塑料覆铝的设计非常前卫，而拉丝阳极化的铝面板更是增强了这款机箱的金属质感。上图是这款机型左侧的散热孔，呈Z字型的散热孔拥有不不同的功效，这点后文将为大家解析。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/023.jpg\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">右侧侧板的散热孔特写，相较左侧侧板简单了一些</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"432\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/024.jpg\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">蜂窝通风孔的设计细节，可以看到COSMOS II的细节设计的相当到位，做工也很精良</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"432\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/025.jpg\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">侧板上的装饰线条也暗藏玄机，这些细节无一不完美的展现了酷冷至尊的工业设计能力</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"432\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/028.jpg\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">侧板解锁机构特写，用户仅需向下一按侧板即可解锁弹开，就像跑车的车门</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"397\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/030.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">在上方是提手，在下方就变成了支架和垫脚，可以看到这个梦幻金属杆与机箱的结合方式</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/031.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">专为下置电源位设计的通风孔位于机箱底板的后方，其中防尘网的加入大大的改善的电源的工作环境，避免了电源变成一台吸尘器，抽取结构的防尘网便于用户除尘维护系统。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/032.jpg\" /></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">橡胶垫脚与机箱的结合采用了螺丝固定的形式，结合紧密非常严谨</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">COSMOS II前脸的冲孔面板仅需从下方向外一翻即可轻松取下进行除尘维护，从上图可以看到这款产品确实表里如一，格栅的加入不仅是为了美观，同时还能起到一点的防护作用。在格栅的后面是这款机箱的前置系统风扇，可以看到酷冷至尊为用户标配了一颗20cm大尺寸风扇，而下面的12cm风扇则为选配。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/034.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">机箱顶部的通风孔挡板同样可以拆卸，不过拆卸前需拧下机箱尾部的一颗手拧螺丝</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/035.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"COSMOS II\" width=\"650\" height=\"449\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://www.itocp.com/html/20120208/aritcle/coolermaster_cosmos2/037.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, ari