op: 0px\">包装清单</td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">机箱本机 x1<br />\r\n            说明书 x1<br />\r\n            保修卡 x1<br />\r\n            螺丝包 x1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-top: 5px\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,247,253); border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\"><b>保修信息</b></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-top: 5px\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 80px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">质保时间</td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">3年</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/915817040/T2TfVYXkXdXXXXXXXX_!!915817040.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/915817040/T2GzYtXoRXXXXXXXXX_!!915817040.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/915817040/T2CjHtXc8aXXXXXXXX_!!915817040.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/915817040/T22aDuXfRXXXXXXXXX_!!915817040.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/915817040/T2HtWYXlVaXXXXXXXX_!!915817040.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/915817040/T2qAHtXcBaXXXXXXXX_!!915817040.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/915817040/T2n6zsXk8aXXXXXXXX_!!915817040.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/915817040/T2nA8.Xj4bXXXXXXXX_!!915817040.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;在DIY装机时我们所选择的<a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\">机箱</a>多为立式机箱，那么立式机箱是最完美的吗？答案当然是否定的，近期酷冷至尊就推出了一款采用家电式箱的机箱产品，它就是酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱，在功能上更为强大，散热效果更佳，比较符合喜欢超频的高端DIY玩家使用。目前，此款机箱已经到货沈阳三好街市场，参考价格为699元，感兴趣的朋友可以多了解一下。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱在设计上并没有采用主流的立式机箱设计，而是将家电式箱的概念引入到机箱的设计理念当中，采用上下分层的结构设计，更加便于机箱的散热，而且还能够瞬间变为超频平台，可谓是极具创新意义，为超频玩家带来了更大的方便。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱前<a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\">面板</a>设计非常细致，面板上覆盖有大面积冲网设计，配合内部安装的两枚进风风扇，可以有效的到达为机箱内部输送新鲜冷空气的效果，而且前面板上设有前置热插拔装置槽及接口适合SSD等存储产品的安装，满足各种高速存储及日常应用的需求。在前置接口方面也提供了两个USB3.0接口及1组音频接口，颇为齐全。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱的除了前面板采用了金属冲网设计外，机箱侧板及上板也都做了大面积的镂空设计，让机箱的散热效果可以到达最佳，此外，顶板上的镂空部分还预留与大尺寸风扇的安装位，如果用户感觉散热能力无法满足的时候，还可以在此进行升级。另外值得一提的是，机箱的两个侧板处还设计凹槽把手，便于用对于机箱进行移动。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 酷冷至尊HAF XB机箱内部分上下两层设计，上层用来安装<a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\">主板</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\">显卡</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170)\">电源</a>以及其他需