 normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; 从上面的图中，能看得出来，其他品牌A这款450W电源在大功耗面前也不示弱，但是当功率超过320W时温控风扇开始提速，噪音很明显的起来了，可见元件温度已经超过平常值。<br />\r\n<img title=\"17.jpg\" alt=\"17.jpg\" width=\"770\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://bbs.coolermaster.com.cn/data/attachment/forum/201203/08/134954smhs28tz8rj2himz.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-s