/www32.tx8cdn.com/photo/dangdang/%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A72%20(3).jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: normal; border-right-width: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block; font-family: \'simsun arial\'; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 12px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://www32.tx8cdn.com/photo/dangdang/%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A72%20(4).jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: normal; border-right-width: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block; font-family: \'simsun arial\'; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 12px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://www32.tx8cdn.com/photo/dangdang/%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A72%20(5).jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: normal; border-right-width: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 0px auto; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block; font-family: \'simsun arial\'; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); font-size: 12px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://www32.tx8cdn.com/photo/dangdang/%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A72%20(6).jpg\" /></p>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold\">在视频安全系统中提高数据存储可靠性。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">使用希捷 SV35 Series 硬盘可符合视频监控存储的行业标准。大容量、监控优化性能和超过 1 百万小时的 MTBF。现在即使在最困难的操作环境下，AcuTrac&trade; 技术也可以提高跟踪的可靠性和性能。<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://www.seagate.com/images/int-ce-sv35.5-overview-1-316x177.png\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">经济高效、超大容量 - 设计用于视频存储应用。</h2>\r\n使用 SV35 Series 硬盘在行业内领先的单碟 1TB 技术来提高每 GB 性能。拥有 1TB、2TB 和 3TB 容量选择和最少的内部构件，SV35 Series 硬盘具有前所未有的大容量、高可靠性和经济性。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">构建更好的监控系统。</h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">希捷 SV35 Series 硬盘特有的强大存储能力和高性能，适用于现代视频监控系统。</p>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">SATA 6Gb/秒接口支持最新、最快的硬盘控制器，同时支持传统的 SATA 1.5Gb/秒和 3Gb/秒控制器</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">领先的单碟 1TB 技术可提供 1TB、2TB 和 3TB 三种容量选择，并拥有更少的机械组件</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">2A 限流和旋转控制功能可进行更多的电源管理，可在归档期间节省电量并提高可靠性</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://www.seagate.com/images/int-ce-sv35.5-overview-2-316x267.png\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">希捷高性能监控存储解决方案。</h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">使用 SV35 Series 硬盘更快的浏览更多数据并支持更多同步摄像机。SV35 Series 硬盘拥有行业内最高的区域密集度，最高可支持每秒 210MB 的数据传输速率。SV35 Series 硬盘拥有全新的双核处理器技术、64MB 高速缓存和监控优化写入缓存管理，适用于高性能监控应用，没有哪个硬盘可以与之相匹敌。</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; pad